  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-6 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A subset of factors are scoped out as not-applicable with explicit documented rationale; all remaining factors are fully assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel. Decision: Accepted.",
